_:N9d0e294050ec41daa76bcaaab1b3c01f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Alison Baptiste is the Director of Public and Security Services at the National Infrastructure and Service Transformation Authority (NISTA).</p>\n\n<p>Alison has extensive strategic and operational project and programme leadership experience gained both in private and public sectors. As Director of Strategy and Investment at the Environment Agency, she led both infrastructure and transformation projects and held senior operational delivery and emergency response roles reporting to COBR. Alison is a Chartered Engineer and Fellow of the Institution of Civil Engineers. Alison was appointed as Commander of the Order of the British Empire for services to the environment in the 2019 New Years Honours.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
